<h2></h2>
<h2>Health Benefits</h2>
The primary health benefit of xanthan gum is it acts as a replacement for gluten. People who suffer from celiac disease or gluten intolerance can enjoy baked food and other items without gluten.

Other health benefits of xanthan gum include
